      "title": "限制与约定",
      "content": "\u003cdiv class=\"table-responsive\"\u003e\n\u003ctable class=\"table table-bordered table-text-center table-vertical-middle\"\u003e\u003cthead\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003cth\u003e测试点编号\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003cth\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-58\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-59\"\u003en\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-20\"\u003en\u003c/script\u003e的规模\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/thead\u003e\u003ctbody\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003e1\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-60\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-61\"\u003en\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-62\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-63\"\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-21\"\u003en \\leq 4\u003c/script\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003e2\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd rowspan=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-64\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-65\"\u003en\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-66\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-67\"\u003e100\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-22\"\u003en \\leq 100\u003c/script\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003e3\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003e4\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\